# School of Metaverse & Virtual Infrastructure

## Purpose
Prepares learners to design and manage virtual learning environments, simulations, and interactive experiences that support measurable learning outcomes.

## Scope
- virtual systems, NPC scripting for instruction, digital twins, learning experience design
- Credentials: certificates and degree pathways
- Delivery: online/hybrid; project-based

## Distinctives
- Instruction-first virtual environment design
- Capstone: deployable virtual learning module + assessment plan